[[!meta title="Version 2.03.41 - Bug Fix Release"]]

Version 2.03.41
===============

* Allow `lvchange --syncaction repair` on RAID LVs with integrity.
* Snapshot merge require exclusive lock on origin.
* Fix adopt result routing in lvmlockd for lockspace start actions.
* Fix more issues found by static analysis.

